        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "slidetitle": "What to Remember",
          "subtitle": "Points to carry forward with you",
          "slidecontent": "• AI can hinder real learning\n• Struggle builds genuine skill\n• Use AI as a tool, not a crutch\n• Check your own understanding first\n• Try the task yourself first",
          "do_not_include": false
